Text: For most women, birth control is completely safe. Some women might experience some side effects like spotting or cramping but they usually go away as the body adjusts. For most of us, the benefits of birth control are way more important than a few side effects. And you might not know this but, some kinds of birth control actually protect against certain types of cancers!
